                        <interp inst="t18471122-name-1339" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM SIMMONDS,</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">Thames police-constable</hi>, 62.) I went to the pri<lb></lb>soner's lodging with the caption—I found the prisoner at the City of London theatre.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18471122-name-1340" type="witnessName">
