                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined. Q.</hi> How did you know it was the prisoner's lodging? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> From the Marine Society's office—I afterwards spoke to the prisoner about the things found in the bundle—he said nothing about them, but on the Sunday morning he told me he took three sovereigns out of my box.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18471122-name-1341" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18471122-name-1341" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18471122-name-1341" type="surname" value="ELTHAM"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18471122-name-1341" type="given" value="CAROLINE"></interp>CAROLINE ELTHAM.</persName>
                  </hi> I am the prisoner's aunt. He brought the bundle to my house at eight o'clock on the Sunday morning—I got an order, and took him to the theater—he told me the captain gave him the boots—there was a crack at the side—I got them mended.</p>
